topic.title: Bojack.Horseman.S03E01.WEBRip.X264-RARBG
topic.body: Meet the most beloved sitcom horse of the '90s - 20 years later. BoJack Horseman was the star of the hit TV show "Horsin' Around," but today he's washed up, living in Hollywood, complaining about everything, and wearing colorful sweaters.
